# Soft Boiled eggs 
##Ingredienses 

- 3 eggs 
- boiling water 
- salt and pepper (for serving)

##instructions 
First you ensure your water is boiling, then softly drop the eggs (at the same time) to the water in a stove. 
Put on a lid. Wait 5-6 minuts (depending on size of eggs). 
At the end, you let out the boiling water and exchange it with cold water. This loses the shell.
